s at any point in the recruitment process read more  related content careers at glencore our graduate rolesglobal opportunities why choose us global network our assetsaround the world explore our global operations glencore at a glance what we doour diverse integrated operations glencore at a glance contact us  glencore home who we are who we are about us about us glencore at a glance our story around the world what we do what we do metals  minerals energy products agriculture marketing  logistics our values our values glencore group policies compliance our board of directors our board of directors board committees governance downloads management structure investors investors rns announcements shareholder centre shareholder centre corporate calendar corporate calendar     share price tools agm agm agm  agm  distribution information distribution information  shareholder faq analyst coverage reports and results reports and results reports reports glencore glencore        xstrata xstrata   reserves  resources transaction archive speeches  presentations speeches  presentations glencore glencore        xstrata xstrata   debt investors debt investors outstanding bonds investor contacts investor contacts subscribe latest consensus estimates sustainability sustainability our sustainability strategy our sustainability strategy our approach to sustainability risk management hsec assurance our people our people our approach safety health workforce society society our approach community engagement creating value for society human rights environment environment our approach environmental management water energy and ghgs land management waste management climate change climate change carbon disclosure reducing emissions helping to shape public policy our business and climate change planning for climate change product stewardship our progress our progress kpis targets external commitments reports presentations case studies case studies       sustainability contacts media media rss f